{"title_page": "Ken-Levi Eikeland", "text_new": "{{short description|Norwegian cyclist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Ken-Levi Eikeland\n| image          = RGP 2018 - 81 Ken-Levi Eikeland.jpg\n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1994|10|9|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Larvik]], Norway\n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| currentteam    = {{ct|FIX}}\n| discipline     = Road\n| role           = Rider\n| ridertype      = \n| amateuryears1  = \n| amateurteam1   = \n| proyears1      = 2016\u2013\n| proteam1       = {{ct|FIX|2016}}\n| majorwins      = \n| medaltemplates = \n| show-medals    = \n}}\n'''Ken-Levi Eikeland''' (born 9 October 1995) is a Norwegian [[bicycle racing|racing cyclist]].<ref name=\"PCS\">{{cite web |url=https://www.procyclingstats.com/rider.php?id=178872 |title=Ken-Levi Eikeland |accessdate=17 September 2017 |work=ProCyclingStats}}</ref> He competed in the [[2017 UCI Road World Championships \u2013 Men's team time trial|men's team time trial]] event at the [[2017 UCI Road World Championships]].<ref name=\"start\">{{cite web |url=https://www.procyclingstats.com/race/World_Championships_-_TTT_2017_Startlist |title=World Championships - TTT Startlist |accessdate=17 September 2017 |work=ProCyclingStats}}</ref>\n\n==Major results==\n;2016\n: 1st Stage 1 [[Carpathian Couriers Race]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{ProCyclingStats|178872}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Eikeland, Ken-Levi}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Norwegian male cyclists]]\n[[Category:People from Larvik]]\n{{Norway-cycling-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Norwegian cyclist}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2017}}\n{{Infobox cyclist\n| name           = Ken-Levi Eikeland\n| image          = RGP 2018 - 81 Ken-Levi Eikeland.jpg\n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and